&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/IO-328&quot; title=&quot;FileUtils.listFilesAndDirs includes original dir in results even when it doesn&amp;#39;t match filter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;IO-328&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;IO-328&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; FileUtils.listFilesAndDirs includes original dir in results even when it doesn&apos;t match filter&lt;br/&gt;
       Javadoc: clarify that original dir is included in the results&lt;/p&gt;

